        <summary>
            Specifies that cookie-based authentication redirects are disabled for an endpoint using <see cref="T:Microsoft.AspNetCore.Http.Metadata.IDisableCookieRedirectMetadata" />.
            When present and not overridden by <see cref="M:Microsoft.AspNetCore.Builder.CookieRedirectEndpointConventionBuilderExtensions.AllowCookieRedirect``1(``0)" /> or <see cref="T:Microsoft.AspNetCore.Http.Metadata.IAllowCookieRedirectMetadata" />,
